ôReiko is Invisible?!ö
ôI love Junko.ö Feeling as though she was hit by a lightening, Reiko was suddenly 
dumped by Tetsuya. From the shock, Reiko's body starts turning invisible. Tetsuya 
and Junko visits the transparent Reiko. Believing that a shock therapy will snap 
Reiko out of her shock, Tetsuya calls her rival, Ayame Kakitsubata. Ayame comes 
to see the transparent Reiko...

